          Our step-by-step guides help both newcomers and long-time residents navigate the complexities of Swiss insurance and financial planning. Each guide provides clear instructions, real-world examples, and expert insights that you won't find elsewhere.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Categories and Guides Section -->
